page.title: 20BROWNIES
page.content: I go to Brownies on Thursdays at Alveston.I enjoy it very much because all you do is play games and have fun. The best game is skipping but I always trip over the rope.We skip through an arch and Brown Owl collects are money.I have already got these badges swimmers,hostess,craft,jester,footpath ,writing and first star.I am now working for my cycling proficiency and second year star.Emma and I both go to brownies together.We are both in the same pack which is called Pixies.There are four packs,the others are Sprites, Elves and gnomes.I am the seconder for the Pixies.Rachel Oxtoby 9 years old.
